Let’s get sculpted using our NEW Tinted Blur Sculpt Stick in the shade Nude Neutral Deep!

🤎 STEP 1: Place stick in the hollow of the cheek to feel where to place your contour 
🤎 STEP 2: Draw a line in the hollow of the cheek, forehead, jawline, eye crease & nose
🤎 STEP 3: Blend using our Blend & Buff Brush in small, circular or tapping motions to create a diffused finish

Did we mention our Tinted Sculpt Stick has blurring pigments to give you a soft-focus filter finish? 👀

Shop Tinted Blur Sculpt Stick, online only at nudestix.com

Sculpt, Bronze and Blush with Nudestix co-founder @taylor_frankel! 

How to MIX YOUR STIX to recreate this sculpted look👇

🤎 Apply our NEW Tinted Blur Sculpt Stick in the shade Nude Neutral Medium to add depth + dimension
🤎 Apply our NEW Tinted Blur Sculpt Stick in the shade Nude Neutral Light to create a softer sculpt 
🤎 Apply our Nudies Bronze in ‘Bondi Bae’ directly above contour placement 
🤎 Blush + Blur by applying our NEW Nudies Matte Lux blurring blush formula in the shade Nude Buff to eyes, lips + cheeks
🤎 Blend everything together using a tapping or circular motion!
